dms-greeter (1:1.0.0ppa1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Greeter extracted from DankMaterialShell into the dank-greeter repository;
    the bash wrapper and /usr/share/quickshell/dms-greeter QML tree are
    replaced by a single Go binary with the Quickshell UI embedded.
  * Existing /etc/greetd/config.toml commands
    (dms-greeter --command COMPOSITOR) keep working unchanged.
  * Epoch 1 introduced: versions restarted at 1.0.0 below the old
    DMS-versioned 1.5.x package.

